{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">EXTRACTO DE DECRETO N&#xBA; 244 EXENTO, DE 2000 </div></div>", "i": 7275483}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Por decreto exento N&#xBA; 244 de fecha 4 de julio de 2000 del Ministerio de Educaci&#xF3;n, se modifica el art&#xED;culo 1&#xBA; del decreto exento de Educaci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 334 de 20 de marzo de 1997, que reconoce oficialmente al Centro de Formaci&#xF3;n T&#xE9;cnica en Servicios de Salud, en el sentido de reemplazar la raz&#xF3;n social del organizador, el domicilio y la actual denominaci&#xF3;n del Centro, por la siguiente:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Nombre de la Instituci&#xF3;n&nbsp;  :&nbsp; &nbsp;  Centro de Formaci&#xF3;n</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  T&#xE9;cnica Cefonor.</div><div class=\"p\">Domicilio&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;  Porras N&#xBA; 586 -</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Antofagasta.</div><div class=\"p\">Organizador&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sociedad Centro de</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Formaci&#xF3;n T&#xE9;cnica</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cefonor Limitada o</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  C.F.T. Cefonor Ltda.</div><br></div>", "i": 7275484}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Santiago, 21 de julio de 2000.- Jos&#xE9; Weinstein Cayuela, Subsecretario de Educaci&#xF3;n.</div><br></div>", "i": 7275485}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctr